Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ALL IN AN INSTANT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A Superior Being is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, hit him in the stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That should force him to spit out Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That kick was a feint!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Warrior Master Style {\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Refractor Fist!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! She knocked Dai free!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Thank goodness he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be thanks to the new clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, it looks like Dai's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu, use one of your items to heal Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My immortal body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam's unbelievably strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And that special attack is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the essence of Grand Master\NBrokin's Warrior Master Style,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and Miss Maam's greatest attack,\Nthe Refractor Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The Refractor Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, your progress\Nhas been beyond impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You've mastered in days what would take\Nnormal Martial Artists years to complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is to teach you my\NWarrior Master Style's greatest skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am ill and feeble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains me that I can't show you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a disappointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Grand Master? What is your illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiaributtitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does Kiari-butt-itis\Nmake you cough?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know you can master it, Maam.\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of skill is it, Grand Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a combination of a certain spell\Nwith the Warrior Master Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grand Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be a Warrior Priest.\NI can't use attack spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack spells aren't the only way\Nto defeat an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That spell is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoimi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoimi is a spell that magically\Nboosts a body's biofunctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, just as plants wither\Nwhen given too much nourishment,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}excessive healing magic\Ncan destroy a body's tissue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, such excessive healing magic\Nwas feared and known as "Mahoimi."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahoimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the most powerful Priests and Sages
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,could wield Mahoimi\Nas a trump card against monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, in time, users of the spell\Nall disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of Magic Power Mahoimi uses\Nis magnitudes above a Behoimi spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, by using healing spells\Nwith the Warrior Master Style Fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I developed the technique to generate\Ndevastating force at the moment of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When used, it creates\Nan overwhelming anti-creature effect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}applying a fatal shock to an enemy's body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fatal to an enemy's body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A truly terrifying skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a terrifying skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those who can understand\Njust how terrifying it is can be taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been called a Grand Master\Nfor decades now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you, Maam, are the first\NI've ever thought worthy to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as your first Master, Aban, trusted\Nyou and gave you the Magic Bullet Gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, trust your kind and just heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I will teach it to you, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Grand Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Miss Maam for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I rescued?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Thanks to Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.\NI didn't know you could fight like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Aren't you supposed\Nto have some item?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, hurry and heal Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a medicinal herb,\Nso be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an antidotal herb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a poison herb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I always carry around\Nfive medicinal herbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used them all when I was attacked by\NTeeny Sangiuni in the mountains!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who uses five whole medicinal herbs\Nagainst such squibs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! It looks like\Nmy brain's still sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have two types of attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacks where your hands glow,\Nand where they don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, that attack can't be used\Nwith your whole body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I deduced it can only be done with your\Nhands, and only at the moment of impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up!\NThat's a special coating mucus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't come off easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If she can't use her glowing fists...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,For me or Dai!\NSomething to heal our stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A Teardrop Acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! Is it useful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As the name implies, it'll cure\Na sparrow's teardrop worth of stamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's enough! That's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that attack, you have nothing\Nthat can hurt my immortal body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Chiu, take me\Nand that acorn up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}REFRACTOR FIST{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}DARK INCENSE{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Get out of there, Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, if you're planning something, hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lot heavier than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't spare the stamina\Nto climb up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to release it\Nall at once at the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching Maam fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized just how wasteful I've been\Nwhile using the power of my crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been fighting\Nwith my power at full throttle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I always use up\Nall my energy in no time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Maam's glowing fists,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I should focus and release\Nall my energy at the moment of impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it's just a little bit of power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if I use it all at the last moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've caused me quite a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious about\Nthat strange attack you used,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but threats like you\Nshould be eliminated on the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's going to the Sword of Champions!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see! Dai's planning to do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do everything I can\Nto distract this thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How typical of you guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You desperately resist,\Neven when you know you're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing more than trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No life is trash!\NNo matter what creature it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't see that,\Nthen you're the real trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Zamuza, you are a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just you. Every creature\Nin this world is a tool for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gain power and knowledge.\NUse it for my benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you're nothing but trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A useless tool\Nis nothing but trash, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My power and mind are the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be the Legion Commander of\Nthe Mystic or Furfang Legion if I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu! Give me that acorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's only a little,\Nbut I feel my strength returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword of Champions, lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat! When did he reach the sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A Mera spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cast a Mera spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure I've got enough Magic Power\Nfor a Mera spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but that won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire it at Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it on the mucus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Refractor Fist!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have into this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Aban...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!\NI'm the ultimate Superior Being!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How can these pieces of trash...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They defeated him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How? How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did my calculations go wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way I could lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Try asking the rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This cornered rat right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What led to my defeat\Nwas assuming lower creatures were trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The error was in my own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Dai!\NThat was an amazing Aban Strash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's thanks to\Nthe Sword of Champions...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! No! The Sword of Champions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the legendary sword\Ncan endure Dai's Dragon power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sword of Champions, much like\Nthe Crown of Champions I gave you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is made from\Nthe legendary metal, Orichalcum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Orichalcum is said to be everlasting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you.\NThat's an elaborate fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Sword of Champions\Nhas already been offered to Lord Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can offer this,\Nmy mission will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,To my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent it to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains the results of\Nmy Superior Being research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as all my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, my father can continue\Nand complete the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You father is Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'll be grateful\Nto you for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My father sees everyone\Nother than himself as tools to be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt he'll shed a tear even if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, despite what he is,\Nhe is still my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Zamuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fate of those\Nwho become Superior Beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When defeated, not even a corpse remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They crumble as black ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's punishment\Nfor toying with the life the gods gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zamuza...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Save me your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite satisfied how things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For just a fleeting moment,\NI had the word's most powerful body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday a complete\NSuperior Being will come defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My... My fight was not in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That right.\NIt could not have been... in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, he probably just\Nwanted to be praised by his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what he said, deep down,\Nhe must have wanted his father's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done! Well done indeed, Zamuza!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life was but a brief 200 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was quite worthwhile!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.49,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be proud in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your research shall produce
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest, most powerful Overfiend\Nin the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:07.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.39,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:19.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:26.65,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:30.37,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:34.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:38.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:42.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:48.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:53.68,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:57.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:22:59.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:03.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:08.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:16.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.50,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai, the Tiny Hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His adventure with his friends has been\Nfilled with battles against powerful enemies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time, a look back on\Nthe trail of Dai's Adventure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:45.61,On Top,,0,0,0,,THE TRAIL OF ADVENTURE, THE PATH FORWARD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
